        },
        "164180981014fd1b1e-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Alvi’s Drift respects (and is committed to protecting) your privacy. Alvi’s Drift thus takes extraordinary steps to handle any personal information collected on this website only in ways compatible with this Privacy Policy.</p><p>This website may collect certain information about your visit, such as the name of the internet service provider and the internet protocol (IP) address through which you access the internet, the date and time you access the site, the page(s) that you visit while on the site, and the internet address of the website from which you linked directly to this site.</p><p>Alvi’s Drift is the sole owner of the information collected on this website. Alvi’s Drift does not (or will never) sell, share, or rent this information to others in ways different from what is disclosed in the privacy statement below. This information is used only to administer this website, analyse trends, and to generally help improve this site, and will never result in your receiving spam e-mails.</p><p><strong>Log Files</strong></p><p>Alvi’s Drift keeps log files on broad fields to track user movements, analyse trends, and gather demographic data. This is not linked to a visitor’s personal identification in any way.</p><p><strong>Cookies & Tracking Technology</strong></p><p>A cookie is a piece of data stored on the visitor’s hard drive containing information about the visitor. Cookies and tracking technologies are useful for gathering information, such as browser types and operating systems, tracking the number of visitors to a website, and understanding how visitors use the websites they browse. This information can help customise a website for specific users. Advertisers connected to Alvi’s Drift might at times require cookies to track statistics about products and locations, but they will not be supplied with any personal identification details of users. However, Alvi’s Drift generally uses cookies for login convenience only.</p><p><strong>Links</strong></p><p>This Privacy Policy applies solely to Alvi’s Drift. Alvi’s Drift is not necessarily aware of, nor is responsible for, differences in privacy statements of external websites linked to or from ours.</p><p><strong>Shopify</strong></p><p>We use Shopify to power our online store. You can read more about how Shopify uses your Personal Information here: <a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/legal/privacy\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://www.shopify.com/legal/privacy</span></a>. When you place an order through our site, we will retain your personal information for our records, unless and until you ask us to erase this information.</p><p><strong>Google Analytics</strong></p><p>We use Google Analytics to help us understand how our customers use the site. You can read more about how Google uses your Personal Information here: <a href=\"https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en</span></a>. You can also opt-out of Google Analytics here: <a href=\"https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout</span></a>.</p><p><strong>Newsletter Registration</strong></p><p>Visitors who registered to receive the Alvi’s Drift newsletter can unsubscribe from this service at any time. Any personal information stored in the Alvi’s Drift database related to the newsletter subscription will be treated as confidential, and will never be shared or sold to any third party.</p><p><strong>WhatsApp Communication Policy</strong></p><p>By opting in via our account registration form, you agree to receive occasional WhatsApp messages from Alvi’s Drift regarding your Private Club Membership and exclusive member benefits. These messages may include service updates, member-specific offers, and important information about your club account. We do not sell alcohol to anyone under the age of 18. By registering, you confirm that you are of legal drinking age. You may opt out of WhatsApp communication at any time by replying “STOP” to any message or by contacting us directly at <a href=\"mailto:marketing@alvisdrift.co.za\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">marketing@alvisdrift.co.za</span></a>.</p><p><strong>Wine Club Registration</strong></p><p>Customers who registered to become members of the Alvi’s Drift Wine Club can unsubscribe from this service at any time. Any personal information stored in the Alvi’s Drift database related to the membership will be treated as confidential and will never be shared or sold to any third party.</p><p><strong>Sharing</strong></p><p>Alvi’s Drift does not harvest the information of third parties when visitors share a page of this website in social circles.</p><p><strong>Changes to This Policy</strong></p><p>Alvi’s Drift may need to update this policy from time to time, in order to address new issues and reflect changes on this website. Please refer back to this policy regularly.</p><p><em><strong>Continued use of this website signifies your acceptance of this Privacy Policy.</strong></em></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>",
            "size": "large"
          }
